text: Fortified by troops, foreboding fencing and police in riot gear, Pres. Trump remained protected from largely peaceful protesters this week—but not from the ire of his predecessors and the nation's top military figures. https://t.co/z1JVPHNOd7

text: An inmate died Wednesday after being pepper sprayed while in his cell at the Metropolitan Detention Center in Brooklyn. A source familiar with the investigation tells @ABC News the inmate died of a heart attack. https://t.co/xAVlugettA
